Budget Rustic Wood Graduation 4 Photo Announcement – Graduation Announcement Cards Popular Budget Rustic Wood Graduation 4 Photo Announcement good product Budget Rustic Wood Graduation 4 Photo Announcement There are many featuresA budget-friendly rustic graduation announcement printed on 4.5×5.6-inch lightweight paper instead of cardstock featuring a brown country wood plank background and 4 pictures of your graduate (a photo collage of 3 pictures on the front and 1 on the back). The back offers an optional text field to include information about your graduate. This design especially complements country, nature or outdoorsman photos. Ideal for conservative budgets and/or hand delivering.
